name: Senior #1 - Rudy
description:
Rudy is a 92-year-old former child star who enjoys golf, listening to techno music and blogging. He is magnetic and creative, but can also be very untrustworthy and a bit destructive.

He didn't finish school. He is a vegan. He has a severe phobia of clowns.

Rudy has one child with his ex-girlfriend’s bestfriend Mimi: Talulah, aged 19.
